    public class OperationException
extends CstaException
    Signals that a CSTA OperationError has occurred. OperationErrors indicate an error in the service request. Applications can catch specific sub-exceptions and/or retrieve the specific CSTA error using the getOperationError method.
    Author:
    Avaya Inc.
    See Also:
    "ECMA-269, sections 9.3 Diagnostic Error Definitions and 12.2.14 ErrorValue", Serialized Form

If the specified cause is null, then the cause string in the detail message is also null. This constructor is useful for exceptions that are little more than wrappers for other throwables.
